{"tid":2376824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最美第三者丨韓韶禧拍劇受傷兼過勞暈倒送院","createTime":"2021-01-23T05:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T00:18:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1728b872cdfb1ef1c93f7d82609e633175e2c9c","tid":2376824,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t1rGgj1tb7qm21j0-ZT7fq_Lu50=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T6IKZH7RERBNBKUOKWS5IS2M7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft1rGgj1tb7qm21j0-ZT7fq_Lu50%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT6IKZH7RERBNBKUOKWS5IS2M7Q.jpg&h=195af936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「小宋慧喬」之稱的韓國話題劇《夫妻的世界》女星韓韶禧（前譯：韓素希）拍畢《夫妻》後人氣急升，早前更升呢做女主角，接拍Netflix新劇《Undercover》，未知是否首次擔正劇集而出盡全力，昨日深夜韓國方面傳來她拍攝《Undercover》時中途受傷兼過勞而暈倒的消息，並因為呼吸困難而被急送到急症室。<br />\n<br />\n大量動作場面<br />\n據了解韓韶禧在《Undercover》中每天都要應付大量的動作戲份，很多時候她都會選擇親身上陣，未有使用替身的情況下進行拍攝，估計她因為每天要參與大量的動作場面，最終過勞體力不支，加上受傷關係而暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n情況並不嚴重<br />\n電視劇製作公司相關人士表示：「在拍攝動作戲時受了傷，從保護演員的角度出發，所以來到了醫院。目前情況並不嚴重，在急症室進行治療。由於明天（23日）沒有拍攝工作，所以至明天為止都會保持她的情況穩定，現在的情況不像大家擔心的那樣嚴重。」<br />\n<br />\n孖安普賢合作<br />\n《Undercover》講述韓韶禧飾演的尹智友，本身是販毒集團成員，但以卧底身份加入警隊，尋找出父親死亡的真相，為在可疑情況下去世的父親報仇，並在復仇的過程中，面對一個個殘酷的真相。而安普賢就演毒品調查科的警長全弼道一角，是一名嚴謹、勇敢、對調查案件相當有決心的角色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rVGUsX3gVCV4H8DaUeufpc6rmII=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6ZJNWFURX5B5BA2WIVC2W6B2PU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrVGUsX3gVCV4H8DaUeufpc6rmII%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6ZJNWFURX5B5BA2WIVC2W6B2PU.jpg&h=c8f958d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sESuRpgRpyDL2cWvX3LoDsZM5A4=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K24JE4F3JBDAZHCTIZBW64636Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsESuRpgRpyDL2cWvX3LoDsZM5A4%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK24JE4F3JBDAZHCTIZBW64636Y.jpg&h=ea0a57a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbac089a8a7d573c3a0965265d72ac87a9da030a","tid":2376824,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"正....期待 Netflix <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n操死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5e976b7de5fb5ed93ac57438dba9dde36d163e","tid":2376824,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"慘慘..."},{"pid":"23a4db9ca237eb31ae85b6b6929d67340f2ea732","tid":2376824,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed5e976b7de5fb5ed93ac57438dba9dde36d163e","tid":2376824,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"慘慘..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca1d004c3928cc3a3eca2a63f8306fcc4e3b60","tid":2376824,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbac089a8a7d573c3a0965265d72ac87a9da030a","tid":2376824,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"正....期待 Netflix <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n操死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/